OL,3,CCharity skinny dip banned due to 1950s
OL,4,Cdecency law
OL,6,FThe first organised community skinny
OL,7,Fdip in Jersey has been banned.
OL,9,FThe charity event planned for Bonne
OL,10,FNuit Bay aimed to raise funds for
OL,11,FJersey Hospice.
OL,13,FWhile the Bailiff and St John
OL,14,FConstable Andy Jehan previously
OL,15,Fapproved it, the swim was subsequently
OL,16,Fcancelled as it would have breached
OL,17,Fthe Policing of Beaches Regulations.
