OL,3,CCharity skinny dip banned due to 1950s
OL,4,Cdecency law
OL,6,FHe says: "They do it in 555 different
OL,7,Flocations in the UK for the Great
OL,8,FBritish Skinny Dip, they also do it in
OL,9,FGuernsey and certainly, standards of
OL,10,Fpublic decency have changed in the
OL,11,Flast 65 years."
OL,13,FJersey Hospice Care also says that any
OL,14,Ffundraising events are vital for their
OL,15,Fwork.
