OL,3,CCharity skinny dip banned due to 1950s
OL,4,Cdecency law
OL,6,FCheri Strudwick from the charity
OL,7,Fexplains: "We've got an ageing
OL,8,Fpopulation in Jersey so demand for
OL,9,Fhospice services is increasing year on
OL,10,Fyear and with that comes an increasing
OL,11,Freliance on fundraising."
OL,13,FDespite this, Constable Jehan has
OL,14,Freaffirmed that he cannot allow an
OL,15,Fevent to take place that would break
OL,16,Fthe law.
OL,18,FHowever, he says that he will speak
OL,19,Fwith legal experts to see how similar
OL,20,Fevents could happen in the future.
